Package Statuses

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StatGet
    Interface to make a HashMap of anonymous functions that refer to a Hero classes getters within the Hero class.
    StatSet
    Interface to make a HashMap of anonymous functions that refer to a Hero classes setters within the Hero class.
    StatusEffectAbility
    This interface provides only one method, getAbilityStatus().
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuffStatus
    BuffStatus extends Status.
    BuffStatuses
    Container class to hold all BuffStatuses.
    BuffStatuses.Defend
    Defend class that ADDS to a hero's defense rating for a duration.
    CrowdControlStatus  
    OffensiveStatusesNotPerTurn
    Container class to hold all OffensiveStatuses that DO NOT tick per turn.
    OffensiveStatusesNotPerTurn.LowerDefense
    LowerDefense class, lowers a heros defense rating.
    OffensiveStatusesPerTurn
    Container class to hold all OffensiveStatuses that tick per turn.
    OffensiveStatusesPerTurn.Poison
    Poison class, damages health.
    OffensiveStatusNotPerTurn
    OffensiveStatusNotPerTurn extends Status.
    OffensiveStatusPerTurn
    OffensiveStatusPerTurn extends Status.
    Status
    Status abstract class.
